\subsection{Method \code{get_ticker()}}{
Get Futures Ticker

Retrieves real-time ticker data for a futures contract.
\subsection{Workflow}{
\enumerate{
\item \strong{Request}: Public GET with the symbol as a query parameter.
\item \strong{Parsing}: Returns a single-row \code{data.table}; coerces \code{ts} from nanoseconds to POSIXct.
}
}

\subsection{API Endpoint}{

\verb{GET https://api.kucoin.com/api/v1/ticker?symbol=\{symbol\}}
}

\subsection{Official Documentation}{

\href{https://www.kucoin.com/docs-new/rest/futures-trading/market-data/get-ticker}{KuCoin Get Ticker}

Verified: 2026-05-23
}

\subsection{Automated Trading Usage}{
\itemize{
\item \strong{Price Monitoring}: Poll the ticker to track best bid/ask spreads and last trade prices for signal
generation.
\item \strong{Execution Timing}: Use \code{side} of the last trade to gauge short-term directional momentum.
\item \strong{Spread Analysis}: Compare \code{best_bid_price} and \code{best_ask_price} to measure market liquidity.
}
}

